# Function to update the chart during sorting
def update_chart(arr, title, delay=0.5):
    plt.bar(range(len(arr)), arr, color='skyblue')
    plt.title(title)
    plt.pause(delay)
    plt.clf()

# Bubble Sort
def bubble_sort(arr):
    arr = arr[:]  # Copy to avoid modifying original list
    n = len(arr)
    for i in range(n):
        for j in range(n - i - 1):
            if arr[j] > arr[j + 1]:
                arr[j], arr[j + 1] = arr[j + 1], arr[j]
    return arr

# Insertion Sort
def insertion_sort(arr):
    arr = arr[:]
    for i in range(1, len(arr)):
        key = arr[i]
        j = i - 1
        while j >= 0 and key < arr[j]:
            arr[j + 1] = arr[j]
            j -= 1
        arr[j + 1] = key
    return arr

# Counting Sort
def counting_sort(arr):
    arr = arr[:]
    max_value = max(arr)
    min_value = min(arr)
    range_of_elements = max_value - min_value + 1
    count = [0] * range_of_elements
    output = [0] * len(arr)

    for num in arr:
        count[num - min_value] += 1

    for i in range(1, len(count)):
        count[i] += count[i - 1]

    for num in reversed(arr):
        output[count[num - min_value] - 1] = num
        count[num - min_value] -= 1

    return output

# Radix Sort
def radix_sort(arr):
    arr = arr[:]
    max_value = max(arr)
    exp = 1
    while max_value // exp > 0:
        counting_sort_radix(arr, exp)
        exp *= 10
    return arr

def counting_sort_radix(arr, exp):
    n = len(arr)
    output = [0] * n
    count = [0] * 10

    for i in range(n):
        index = (arr[i] // exp) % 10
        count[index] += 1

    for i in range(1, 10):
        count[i] += count[i - 1]

    for i in range(n - 1, -1, -1):
        index = (arr[i] // exp) % 10
        output[count[index] - 1] = arr[i]
        count[index] -= 1

    for i in range(n):
        arr[i] = output[i]

# Bucket Sort
def bucket_sort(arr):
    arr = arr[:]
    bucket_count = len(arr) // 2
    buckets = [[] for _ in range(bucket_count)]

    min_value, max_value = min(arr), max(arr)
    range_of_elements = max_value - min_value

    for num in arr:
        index = int(bucket_count * (num - min_value) / (range_of_elements + 1))
        buckets[index].append(num)

    for bucket in buckets:
        bucket.sort()

    sorted_array = []
    for bucket in buckets:
        sorted_array.extend(bucket)

    return sorted_array

# Bubble Sort Visualization
def bubble_sort_visual(arr):
    arr = arr[:]
    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 5))
    for i in range(len(arr)):
        for j in range(len(arr) - i - 1):
            if arr[j] > arr[j + 1]:
                arr[j], arr[j + 1] = arr[j + 1], arr[j]
                update_chart(arr, "Bubble Sort Visualization")
    plt.bar(range(len(arr)), arr, color='green')
    plt.title("Bubble Sort Completed")
    plt.show()

# Insertion Sort Visualization
def insertion_sort_visual(arr):
    arr = arr[:]
    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 5))
    for i in range(1, len(arr)):
        key = arr[i]
        j = i - 1
        while j >= 0 and key < arr[j]:
            arr[j + 1] = arr[j]
            j -= 1
            update_chart(arr, "Insertion Sort Visualization")
        arr[j + 1] = key
    plt.bar(range(len(arr)), arr, color='green')
    plt.title("Insertion Sort Completed")
    plt.show()

# Counting Sort Visualization
def counting_sort_visual(arr):
    arr = arr[:]
    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 5))
    max_value = max(arr)
    min_value = min(arr)
    count = [0] * (max_value - min_value + 1)
    
    for num in arr:
        count[num - min_value] += 1

    sorted_arr = []
    for i in range(len(count)):
        while count[i] > 0:
            sorted_arr.append(i + min_value)
            count[i] -= 1
            update_chart(sorted_arr + arr[len(sorted_arr):], "Counting Sort Visualization")

    plt.bar(range(len(sorted_arr)), sorted_arr, color='green')
    plt.title("Counting Sort Completed")
    plt.show()

# Radix Sort Visualization
def radix_sort_visual(arr):
    arr = arr[:]
    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 5))
    max_value = max(arr)
    exp = 1
    while max_value // exp > 0:
        counting_sort_radix(arr, exp)
        update_chart(arr, "Radix Sort Visualization")
        exp *= 10
    plt.bar(range(len(arr)), arr, color='green')
    plt.title("Radix Sort Completed")
    plt.show()

# Bucket Sort Visualization
def bucket_sort_visual(arr):
    arr = arr[:]
    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 5))
    bucket_count = len(arr) // 2
    buckets = [[] for _ in range(bucket_count)]

    min_value, max_value = min(arr), max(arr)
    range_of_elements = max_value - min_value

    for num in arr:
        index = int(bucket_count * (num - min_value) / (range_of_elements + 1))
        buckets[index].append(num)
        update_chart(arr, "Bucket Sort (Filling Buckets)")

    sorted_array = []
    for bucket in buckets:
        bucket.sort()
        sorted_array.extend(bucket)
        update_chart(sorted_array + arr[len(sorted_array):], "Bucket Sort (Sorting Buckets)")

    plt.bar(range(len(sorted_array)), sorted_array, color='green')
    plt.title("Bucket Sort Completed")
    plt.show()
